trans-unit.source: Represents a row in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en rad i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: In this topic: - [Introduction](#introduction) - [Declarative Syntax](#declarative_syntax) ## Introduction The TableRow class represents a row in a control.
trans-unit.target: I dette emnet:- [Introduksjon](#introduction) - [deklarerende syntaksen](#declarative_syntax) ## innføring i TableRow klassen representerer en rad i en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: This class allows you to control how the contents of the row are displayed.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan du angi hvordan innholdet i raden som skal vises.

trans-unit.source: The alignment of the contents in the row are specified by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.HorizontalAlign%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.VerticalAlign%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Justering av innholdet i raden er angitt ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.HorizontalAlign%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.VerticalAlign%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.VerticalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.HorizontalAlign%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can programmatically manage the cells in the row by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Du kan programmatisk administrere cellene i raden med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A> collection is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> objects that represent the cells in the row.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A>samlingen er en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>objekter som representerer cellene i raden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow.Cells%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> control can be used to display user input, which might include malicious client script.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>kontrollen kan brukes til å vise brukerinndata, som kan inneholde skadelig klienten skript</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>

trans-unit.source: Check any information that is sent from a client for executable script, SQL statements, or other code before displaying it in your application.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller informasjonen som ble sendt fra en klient for kjørbare skript, SQL-setninger eller annen kode før det blir vist i programmet.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET provides an input request validation feature to block script and HTML in user input.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET gir et inndataforespørselen valideringsfunksjonen til å blokkere skript og HTML i brukerinndata.

trans-unit.source: Validation server controls are also provided to assess user input.
trans-unit.target: Validering serverkontroller leveres også for å vurdere brukerinndata.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [ASP.NET Validation Controls](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [ASP.NET validering Kontroller](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the horizontal alignment of the contents in the row.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir vannrett justering av innholdet i raden.

trans-unit.source: Use the HorizontalAlign property to specify the horizontal alignment of the contents of the row.
trans-unit.target: Bruk HorizontalAlign-egenskapen til å angi vannrett justering av innholdet i raden.

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the possible values.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser mulige verdier.

trans-unit.source: |Horizontal Alignment|Description| |--------------------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The horizontal alignment is not set.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The contents of the row are left justified.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The contents of the row are centered.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The contents of the row are right justified.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The contents of the row are uniformly spread out and aligned with both the left and right margins.|

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the control should set the <xref uid="langword_csharp_disabled" name="disabled" href=""></xref> attribute of the rendered HTML element to "disabled" when the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.IsEnabled*> property is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om kontrollen skal angi den <xref uid="langword_csharp_disabled" name="disabled" href=""> </xref> attributtet i det gjengitte HTML-elementet til "deaktivert" når kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.IsEnabled*>egenskapen <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.IsEnabled*>

trans-unit.source: This property indicates how ASP.NET should render HTML for a control when the control is disabled.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir hvordan ASP.NET skal gjengi HTML for en kontroll når kontrollen er deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: If this property is `true`, ASP.NET renders a `disabled` attribute when a control is disabled.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er `true`, ASP.NET gjengir en `disabled` attributt når en kontroll er deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: If this property is `false`, ASP.NET renders a `class` attribute when a control is disabled.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er `false`, ASP.NET gjengir en `class` attributt når en kontroll er deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.SupportsDisabledAttribute%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.SupportsDisabledAttribute%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.SupportsDisabledAttribute%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property indicates an ASP.NET version lower than `4.0`; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen angir en ASP.NET-versjonen som er lavere enn `4.0`; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the TableSection property to get or set where the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> object is placed in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk TableSection-egenskapen for å hente eller angi der den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>objektet er plassert i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>

trans-unit.source: For the available table locations, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection> for tilgjengelig tabell-plasseringer

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the possible values.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser mulige verdier.

trans-unit.source: |Table row section|Displayed as| |-----------------------|------------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>|The header row.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>|The body of the table.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>|The footer row.| When using the declarative syntax, the sections must be in the order of header, body, and then footer.
trans-unit.target: | Tabellen rad-delen | Vises som | |-----------------------|------------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>| Overskriftsraden. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>| Meldingsteksten i tabellen. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>| Bunntekstraden. | Når du bruker syntaksen deklarerende, delene må være i rekkefølgen topptekst, body og bunntekst.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection> enumeration enables you to build accessible Web sites using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control by adding the `<thead>`, `<tbody>`, and `<tfoot>` elements to the HTML that is rendered to the client.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>opplisting gjør mulig å bygge tilgjengelig webområder ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontrollen ved å legge til den `<thead>`, `<tbody>`, og `<tfoot>` elementer til HTML gjengis til klienten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRowSection>

trans-unit.source: If all rows in a table are in the `<tbody>` element, the section information is not rendered.
trans-unit.target: Hvis alle radene i en tabell i det `<tbody>` elementet delen informasjonen er ikke gjengis.

trans-unit.source: At least one row must be in a non-body element.
trans-unit.target: Minst én rad må være et ikke-body-element.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.target: Bruk VerticalAlign-egenskapen til å angi den loddrette justeringen av innholdet i raden.
